<p>January 7, 2019 (SAINT PAUL) â Keith Ellison was sworn in today as Minnesotaâs 30th Attorney General. In brief inaugural remarks, Attorney General Ellison declared, âMy job as the Peopleâs Lawyer is to help Minnesotans afford their lives and live with dignity and respect. â¦ The Minnesota Attorney Generalâs office will be the place where everybody counts and everybody matters.â</p>
