<p class="center"> * * * * *</p>
<p> <em>Inaugural remarks of Attorney General Keith Ellison, as prepared for delivery</em></p>
<p> Let me tell you about Alex Smith. He worked hard as a restaurant manager. He had a dream of owning his own one day. He was loved by his family and friends.</p>
