<p> My job as the Peopleâs Lawyer is to help Minnesotans like Alex afford their lives and live with dignity and respect.</p>
<p> In this time of the worst income inequality in America in a century, one of the last bastions of power for regular people is our democracy.</p>
<p> But the demands of profit over people are putting pressure on our democracy.</p>
<p> As the Peopleâs Lawyer, the Minnesota Attorney Generalâs Office will be the place â as it has been from Walter Mondale to Lori Swanson â where we protect the rights of the people.</p>
